  "general_provisions": "This bill amends provisions related to homeless services.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines and amends terms;<hr><ltbullet>repeals certain obsolete sections of code;<hr><ltbullet>amends the duties of the Office of Homeless Services (office) and duties of the homeless services coordinator (coordinator);<hr><ltbullet>amends certain staffing requirements for certain boards or committees;<hr><ltbullet>amends certain reporting requirements; <hr><ltbullet>permits a service provider to temporarily expand a congregate shelter's bed capacity limit under certain conditions;<hr><ltbullet>changes provisions related to a participating local government's tax revenue distributions for homeless shelters; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
